          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/78485297-mario-the-lone-bookwolf?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/78485297-mario-the-lone-bookwolf?shelf=butcher-jim">butcher-jim</a>
